thread.title_full: Trustpilot UK reviewed by Carlos Dyer

author: Carlos Dyer
title: Carlos Dyer
text:
there is no room for second best
but as you train hard and well to be exceptionally first
its already written within thy signature what u are
so to second guess your only core ability
is like looking in the mirror & forgetting that amazing image one saw in full view
so count your blessings one by one
for you have learnt one of lives most precious secrets to growth & productivity to move steadily discerning & wise so u miss nothing a long the way
but soak up what is needed to maintain a conquerors lifestyle
situations circumstances issues represent many mountains you have already overcome & conquered I wish you the very best for the future as your light shines out of your heart brighter and brighter
